Metadata: California Sea Grant College Program 1978-1980 Biennial Report
University of California Sea Grant College Program
program reports (annual, progress, planning reports, etc)

This report on the California Sea Grant College Program, covering the fiscal years 1978-1979 and 1979-1980. It covers the period October 1, 1978 to September 30, 1980 and contains brief technical reports on all of the projects in the program supported during that period.
